\documentclass main: qsd_response_geometry.tex
Figures: figures/{scalar_fold,channel_split,fold_example}.pdf, unbounded_qsd_lyapunov.png
Bibliography: embedded (thebibliography); no external .bib.
Engine: pdflatex (two passes; standard TeX Live, no nonstandard packages).
Ancillary files (anc/): Lean 4 rational-core kernels (UnboundedLyapunovKernel.lean,
  InfiniteDimQSDKernel.lean) with scope tables (MAPPING.md, AXIOMS.md); the verification
  script (verify_identities.py); the figure scripts; and the walkthrough notebook
  (qsd_response_geometry_walkthrough.ipynb). The Lean layer checks only rational cores over Q.
